#. module: escape_rooms
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:escape_rooms.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This app makes scheduling intuitive for customers and efficient for your "
"team. Whether it’s a small group or a company team-building event, players "
"can choose their preferred slot, answer custom questions, and receive "
"instant confirmations. It’s all synced behind the scenes with room capacity."
msgstr ""
"Denne app gør aftaleplanlægning intuitiv for kunderne og effektiv for dit "
"team. Uanset om det er en lille gruppe eller en større teambuilding-"
"begivenhed, kan deltagerne vælge deres foretrukne tidspunkt, besvare "
"individuelle spørgsmål og straks modtage en bekræftelse – alt imens appen "
"automatisk synkroniserer med rumkapaciteten i baggrunden."

#. module: escape_rooms
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:escape_rooms.welcome_article_body
msgid "Track sales per staff member with <strong>session reports</strong>."
msgstr "Brug <strong>sessionrapporter</strong> til at spore medarbejdersalg."

#. module: escape_rooms
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:escape_rooms.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use <strong>custom questions</strong> during booking to tailor the "
"experience (e.g. birthday surprise? team-building?)."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong>brugerdefinerede spørgsmål</strong> ved booking for at tilpasse "
"oplevelsen individuelt (f.eks. fødselsdagsoverraskelse eller teambuilding)."

#. module: escape_rooms
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:escape_rooms.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use <strong>pipelines</strong> to track enquiry &gt; quote &gt; contract "
"&gt; event."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong>pipelines</strong> til at følge processen fra forespørgsel &gt; "
"tilbud &gt; kontrakt og arrangement."

